OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776679573
OL,3,CSister's tribute to former BBC DJ and
OL,4,CLive Aid presenter Andy Kershaw
OL,6,FBroadcaster Liz Kershaw has described
OL,7,Fher brother Andy Kershaw as her "best
OL,8,Ffriend" after the former BBC Radio 1
OL,9,Fdied at the age of 66.
OL,11,FThe DJ, who was born in Rochdale, was
OL,12,Fbest known for his Radio 1 show which
OL,13,Fran from 1985 to 2000.
OL,15,FIt was revealed in January that
OL,16,FKershaw was undergoing cancer
OL,17,Ftreatment after tumours which were
OL,18,Fseverely limiting his mobility were
OL,19,Fdiscovered in his spine last August.
OL,26,@oD@aOUpD@GO]
