PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776679573
OL,3,CSister's tribute to former BBC DJ and
OL,4,CLive Aid presenter Andy Kershaw
OL,6,FWriting on X, Liz Kershaw, who is
OL,7,Fherself one of the longest serving
OL,8,Ffemale national radio DJs in the UK,
OL,9,Fthanked people for getting in touch
OL,10,Ffollowing his death.
OL,12,F"Thank you for all your messages of
OL,13,Faffection for Our Andrew and kindness
OL,14,Ftoday. I've lost my best friend," she
OL,15,Fwrote.
OL,17,FShe also posted a photo with her arm
OL,18,Faround her younger brother several
OL,19,Fyears ago.
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@aO]
