PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776679573
OL,3,CSister's tribute to former BBC DJ and
OL,4,CLive Aid presenter Andy Kershaw
OL,6,FKershaw also documented radio diaries
OL,7,Ffrom North Korea which, according to
OL,8,Fthe BBC, were among the first
OL,9,Fprogrammes to be recorded inside the
OL,10,Fcountry.
OL,12,FThe broadcaster received multiple Sony
OL,13,FRadio Academy Awards throughout his
OL,14,Fcareer, and was celebrated for
OL,15,Fbringing world music and specialised
OL,16,Fgenres to mainstream radio.
OL,18,FAmong the tributes, fans described how
OL,19,Fhe had been 'the soundtrack to so many
OL,20,Flives'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
