PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776679573
OL,3,CSister's tribute to former BBC DJ and
OL,4,CLive Aid presenter Andy Kershaw
OL,6,FRecounting how he hadn't completed his
OL,7,Fdegree at Leeds Uni because of his
OL,8,Flove of music, he said he had been
OL,9,F'busy being student union entz sec: "
OL,10,FI gave it up for music and the free
OL,11,Felectric band".
OL,13,FBBC News Presenter Clive Myrie, who is
OL,14,Ffrom Bolton, said: "Andy was a huge
OL,15,Finspiration to me as a Northern
OL,16,Fworking class kid with flat vowels."
OL,26,@qD@eOUsD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
