FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776679573
OL,3,CSister's tribute to former BBC DJ and
OL,4,CLive Aid presenter Andy Kershaw
OL,6,F"The only person on network BBC TV and
OL,7,Fradio who sounded like me. His sister
OL,8,FLiz Kershaw won Celebrity Mastermind
OL,9,Fthe other day- so a brainy couple of
OL,10,FLancastrians! My favourite kind. RIP".
OL,12,FThe veteran DJ joined BBC Radio 3 in
OL,13,F2001 but left the post in 2007, having
OL,14,Ffaced a series of personal problems
OL,15,Fafter his long-term relationship broke
OL,16,Fdown and he was jailed after breaking
OL,17,Fa restraining order.
OL,19,FKershaw was in a 17-year relationship
OL,20,Fwith Juliette Banner, and the pair had
OL,21,Ftwo children together.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
