FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776679573
OL,3,CSister's tribute to former BBC DJ and
OL,4,CLive Aid presenter Andy Kershaw
OL,6,FThe couple lived on the Isle of Man
OL,7,Ftogether before eventually separating.
OL,9,FHe later returned to the BBC in 2010
OL,10,Fto host its Music Planet programme
OL,11,Falongside Lucy Duran, and again in
OL,12,F2020 for a brief stint on Radio 3
OL,13,Fpresenting The Kershaw Tapes.
OL,15,FKershaw continued his career as a
OL,16,Fbroadcaster in recent years, having
OL,17,Flaunched his own podcast which
OL,18,Ffeatured guests such as Robyn
OL,19,FHitchcock, The Burner Band and Martin
OL,20,FCarthy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
